{"tid":113894,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食左豬膶十幾年 味食過咁既樣既","createTime":"2017-02-09T10:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T14:18:58.000Z","uid":83707,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eabfb0aca1fd6aa62d62373e807448e11b620aca","tid":113894,"uid":83707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/09/183443_52eeee06f4f486c8b9180c02755c34b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F09%2F183443_52eeee06f4f486c8b9180c02755c34b7.jpg&h=f6406a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6ZJvmS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6ZJvmS.jpg&h=ea3b4016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食食下 第一碗黑色果到仲大<br />\n呀叔食左十幾年三哥 無食過呢舊<br />\n同班呀姐講 <br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   呀姐：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：點解舊豬膶咁既<br />\n呀姐：無事嫁<br />\n我：食左幾廿年譚仔都味食過咁<br />\n呀姐：我幫你換過碗<br />\n<br />\n之後換完都係咁<br />\n呀姐話係大風吹乾左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036fe559df14470960e4981523e3984e002d17e7","tid":113894,"uid":60118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:46:23.000Z","msg":"吹乾&hellip;乜呀姐咁有創意"},{"pid":"925153b7d5101784ade99e491a0a5f79c35ecab2","tid":113894,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"豬潤咁細"},{"pid":"e112dcb432db4b1082fa260e098b332cdfd289fc","tid":113894,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"多左幾啖阿姐口水"},{"pid":"93fd66050c1637dcaa34aaf87cf37a7f6b9c1b4b","tid":113894,"uid":77951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"阿姐既體汁"},{"pid":"0bdbabbe230d38cf1f023d64204546